  "description": "The sun dipped below the horizon, casting a crimson hue over the sprawling vineyard of Château Fleur. The estate buzzed with anticipation for the annual wine-tasting gala, but as guests swirled their glasses, an ear-piercing scream shattered the evening calm.",
